description:
a photo series from my last exhibition "LATAR BELAKANG" in 2018

I imagine myself in a crowd of strangers and unable to interact.
My existence only comes at a glance, a fraction of a second in their lives, unseen, never present.

That’s what I imagine had been perceived by the objects that I find everywhere,
Exist, but never really present in our lives until you gave it a background.
